        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "### All 11 Species (Nodes) in the Network\n\n| # | Species | Equilibrium | log K | Phase |\n|---|---------|-------------|-------|-------|\n| 1 | **Zn²⁺** (free metal ion) | — | — | aqueous |\n| 2 | **OH⁻** (free ligand) | — | — | aqueous |\n| 3 | **Zn(OH)⁺** | Zn²⁺ + OH⁻ ⇌ Zn(OH)⁺ | **4.70** | aqueous |\n| 4 | **Zn(OH)₂ (aq)** | Zn²⁺ + 2 OH⁻ ⇌ Zn(OH)₂ | **−10.2** | aqueous |\n| 5 | **Zn(OH)₃⁻** | Zn²⁺ + 3 OH⁻ ⇌ Zn(OH)₃⁻ | **13.9** | aqueous |\n| 6 | **Zn(OH)₄²⁻** | Zn²⁺ + 4 OH⁻ ⇌ Zn(OH)₄²⁻ | **15.5** | aqueous |\n| 7 | **Zn(OH)₂ (s, amorphous)** | Zn(OH)₂(s,am) ⇌ Zn²⁺ + 2 OH⁻ | **−14.82** | solid |\n| 8 | **Zn(OH)₂ (s, β₁)** | Zn(OH)₂(s,β₁) ⇌ Zn²⁺ + 2 OH⁻ | **−15.54** | solid |\n| 9 | **Zn(OH)₂ (s, β₂)** | Zn(OH)₂(s,β₂) ⇌ Zn²⁺ + 2 OH⁻ | **−15.50** | solid |\n| 10 | **Zn(OH)₂ (s, γ)** | Zn(OH)₂(s,γ) ⇌ Zn²⁺ + 2 OH⁻ | **−15.56** | solid |\n| 11 | **ZnO (s)** | ZnO(s) + H₂O ⇌ Zn²⁺ + 2 OH⁻ | **−15.96** | solid |\n\n*(Additional solid polymorphs: δ at log K = −15.45 and ε at log K = −15.77 are also included as distinct nodes.)*",
